		{
			description: [
				"Aquatic invertebrates. They can't survive on land."
				""
				"Tameable with tropical fish. They have the same commands as eagles. Since fists of mantis shrimp are so powerful they can set enemies on fire, they're pretty good at defending you."
				""
				"Shift RMB to give the shrimp the block in your hand. The shrimp will start exploring and break blocks identical to the one in its hands, which allows for some low-level automation!"
