					}
				}
				id: "62B3B2BA2580CF45"
				observe_type: 5
				timer: 0L
				title: "Crab"
				to_observe: "quark:crab"
				type: "observation"
			}]
			x: 3.0d
			y: -1.0d
		}
		{
			description: ["Despite the cool name of Lionfish, these fish are actually quite generic. They can be found in warm oceans and will poison you if you get too close. They can also be rarely reeled in with a fishing rod. "]
