		}
		{
			description: [
				"These very common crabs spawn on beaches and can sometimes appear when a coconut falls from a tree."
				""
				"They mostly just roam around, but if you hit them enough, they will drop coconut slices. Coconut slices can be cooked in a cooking pot to create coconut curry or tropical stew. You can also use eaten coconut slices as bowls for a few different stew items."
				""
				"If you kill one of these crabs, you can obtain a crab claw, which can be used as shears or cooked for crab meat. The crab claw is also an ingredient in the Tide Trident."
			]
			id: "40CB201941711906"
			invisible: true
			tasks: [{
