		{
			description: [
				"This little version of the leviathan are found by hatching the Abyssal Egg, dropped by adult Leviathans. These creatures can be tamed with tropical fish."
				""
				"Despite their size and age, baby leviathans have lots of health, and regenerate quickly when hurt."
				""
				"They have a purple laser attack which deals large amounts of damage, and move quickly, making them one of the best pets in Mincemeat."
			]
