		{
			description: [
				"These upgrades of trident drowned are found in deep oceans and attack those who get near. They sometimes drop coral spears and nautilus shells. "
				""
				"These deeplings have not proven themselves in combat, and as such use rudimentary spears made from coral. They hope to defeat aloof travelers so they will be gifted a better weapon."
			]
			id: "55AD09DC5242B726"
			invisible: true
			tasks: [{
				icon: {
					Count: 1
