			}]
			x: -1.0d
			y: -2.0d
		}
		{
			description: [
				"These deeplings are proficient in Riptide and wield glaives instead of the spears their subordinates use."
				""
				"They have mastered every form of attacking with their weapon, being able to propel themselves through the water, attack up close, or from a distance by throwing it."
				""
				"Deepling brutes don't like being on land, since they'll suffocate after spending too much time there. This means finding an island or digging beneath the ocean are good forms of escape."
				""
				"To kill a brute, never stop moving. They can be bested by filling them up with arrows. If you can't find land, be sure to never stop moving and parry their attacks since you can't dodge underwater."
				""
				"They sometimes drop a coral bardiche, which are more powerful but slower than tridents."
			]
			id: "5C4E6500E68A91C6"
			invisible: true
			tasks: [{
