		{
			description: [
				"These stealthy secret agents are hard to discover in the wild, sometimes acting like alligators in rivers to avoid being spotted during their top-secret missions. If you do spot one and attempt to get too close, they will inject you with a poisonous serum to neutralize you."
				""
				"A sad truth about these agents is that there are very few missions for them, so they are always strapped for cash. Because of this, you can give them some Redstone or a Redstone block to have them work for you and locate clay. If they find the clay, they will start digging into it, pulling out maggots and sometimes even a nice fedora."
			]
			id: "7D62F8EA0309690C"
			invisible: true
			tasks: [{
				icon: {
