				type: "observation"
			}]
			x: -7.0d
			y: 1.0d
		}
		{
			description: [
				"This unique squid can be found by fishing in the water, but you can't get it by killing a regular squid. Regular squids are not great food, often causing hunger if eaten. However, the rare glow squid gives night vision instead of hunger."
				""
				"These squids are excellent cooking ingredients. You can cook them in a furnace or frying pan to create baked squid. They can also be used in a cooking pot with other ingredients to make stuffed squid. If you prefer not to cook this cute little squid whole, you can remove its tentacles and cook them separately to create fried tentacles or use them in a pot to make takoyaki."
			]
			id: "3AA03B67C0184E0B"
			invisible: true
			tasks: [
