		{
			description: [
				"This huge fish, found at the bottom of the frozen ocean below an ice maze, is a dangerous threat, capable of killing you very quickly if you are not careful. When it sees a player, it will wait a few seconds and then dash very quickly at the player, dealing very high damage."
				""
				"The key to killing the angler fish is by drawing it out of the water with a vine lasso or motor grappling hook or by swimming right up to it and trying to deal as much DPS as you can. "
				""
				"After killing it, it will drop esca, which can be used to make underwater torches and is a part of a few food items. "
				""
				"It will also drop an angler fang, which can be used to make the Terrible Armor and two weapons: the Poisoned Sword and Poisoned Chakram."
			]
			id: "269CF108719CCF44"
			invisible: true
			tasks: [{
