		{
			description: [
				"These Florida citizens are found lurking in rivers or wetlands and will bite animals or humans and start spinning rapidly. "
				""
				"While they are spinning, they deal very high damage and will continue spinning unless you sneak, which may give you a few seconds to get away."
				""
				"If you kill this Floridian, they will drop some of their super sunburned crocodile scutes, which can be made into a crocodile chestplate. Although it sounds impressive, it simply raises your swimming speed."
