		{
			description: [
				"Cats don't like being in the water, which must be an anomaly."
				""
				"These cats in the water swim around without a care in the world and don't do much. However, they do taste really good. If you try chopping them up, they will drop their insides, which is likely kind of gross and hairy."
				""
				"Fun fact: catfish are also toxic in the real world. Some catfish can get quite big and have over 30 base HP. If you find one, you're pretty lucky."
