		{
			description: [
				"Aquamancers are masters of the aquatic craft. They're found in their towers on beaches and are a bit misanthropic because they're going through some unwanted changes."
				""
				"Unlike most mages, aquamancers are proficient in two schools of magic: aqua and lightning. They'll try and chase you out of their towers using a variety of spells like Bubble Spray, Hydro Shot, Rainfall, Shockwave, and Ball Lightning."
				""
				"Aquamancers differ in the loot they drop. You can find an Aqua Rune, ink, and some scrolls like usual, but also some Augments, which are nice if you're looking to build around the Aqua, Ice, or Lightning schools."
			]
			id: "2D40306B72237CC0"
